==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Slating
<hw>Slat"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of covering
with slate, slates, or a substance resembling slate; the work of a
slater.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Slates, collectively; also, material for
slating.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slatt</ent>⟦br⟧
